window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>You will take this bride, to have and to hold, from this day forward, until death do you part. This will be your solemn vow; you have no choice.</b></p> <p>Trapped in a twisted and dark courtship with a secret woman who needs my strength to survive, I will be wed. Walking the thin line between lunacy and reality, I am now the protector of my future captive bride.</p> <p>So I have no choice but to recite the vows: I take thee. In this arranged matrimony. Until we are parted by death.</p>"; 
